articles.title: Trump repeals tariffs on some foods as Americans face high grocery prices - The Washington Post
articles.description: President rolls back import levies on beef, tomatoes, coffee and a host of other agricultural goods after administration officials signaled coming changes aimed at addressing consumer complaints about high food costs.
